Hi there, we're [[*user FLOORBOARDS]], recovering New Weird junkie and aspiring professional writer. Our biggest influences are H.P. Lovecraft, Kurt Vonnegut, David Lynch, and Wes Anderson. We hope you've enjoyed the articles we've written for this site! If so, you can also support us either through our [*https://roxanne-wormwood.bandcamp.com Bandcamp] or our [https://ko-fi.com/roxannewormwood Ko-Fi].

For my author will: In the event you don't hear from me in 3 years, please direct any requests to edit or move my pages towards [[*user TealQuacks]]. 

Finally, please check out the writings of [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/natalie-watts NatVoltaic], [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/floppyphoenix Lt. Flops], [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/liryn Liryn], and [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/uraniumempire UraniumEmpire], in no particular order, who are amazing authors with similar styles to mine.

Thank you <3

